{"title":"Podcast #109: Gravel Talk with Alexey Vermeulen & Pearl Izumi & Sir Willie the Wiener!","link":"https://bikerumor.com/bikerumor-podcast-109-alexey-vermeulen/","date":1748627278000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/fox-bill-brown-podcast-interview-1536x1024.webp\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1024\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>Jordan sits down with professional gravel race extraordinaire <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/alexeyvermeulen/?hl=en\">Alexey Vermeulen</a> and Pearl Izumi product line manager Lani Benson. They unpack how gravel gear (especially kit and outerwear) has evolved along with the sport’s progression. But that’s just the tip of the iceberg. Listen Here!</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><div>\n<div></div>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Welcome to Episode 109! </h2>\n\n\n\n<p>It’s not all gear and geeking out. However, the conversation moves into the <em>“real meaning”</em> of gravel. Why would someone subject themselves to a grueling (yet fun) 10-hour day on the bike? </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/CREDIT_-Nolan-Carney.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2500\" height=\"1667\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/CREDIT_-Nolan-Carney.webp\" alt=\"CREDIT_ Nolan Carney\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/CREDIT_-Nolan-Carney.webp 2500w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/CREDIT_-Nolan-Carney-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/CREDIT_-Nolan-Carney-1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/CREDIT_-Nolan-Carney-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/CREDIT_-Nolan-Carney-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/CREDIT_-Nolan-Carney-2048x1366.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/CREDIT_-Nolan-Carney-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/CREDIT_-Nolan-Carney-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><br />Importantly, how that day on the bike might not vibe with the most obvious gear choice. For example, the super lightweight, stiff-soled gear the professionals are racing might not be the best for you. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><div>\n\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The group discusses their favorite pieces of gravel (and all-around kit) from the newest Pearl Izumi offerings, as well as Alexey’s enduring love for the Attak Barrier jacket.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/PRO-Alpha-Layer.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/PRO-Alpha-Layer.webp\" alt=\"PRO Alpha Layer\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/PRO-Alpha-Layer.webp 1000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/PRO-Alpha-Layer-297x297.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/PRO-Alpha-Layer-120x120.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/PRO-Alpha-Layer-768x768.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Transfer-Mesh-SL-Base-layer-lifestyle.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1536\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Transfer-Mesh-SL-Base-layer-lifestyle-1536x1536.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Transfer-Mesh-SL-Base-layer-lifestyle-1536x1536.png 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Transfer-Mesh-SL-Base-layer-lifestyle-297x297.png 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Transfer-Mesh-SL-Base-layer-lifestyle-120x120.png 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Transfer-Mesh-SL-Base-layer-lifestyle-768x768.png 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Transfer-Mesh-SL-Base-layer-lifestyle.png 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/AmfibLobsterEvoGlove_hero.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1536\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/AmfibLobsterEvoGlove_hero-1536x1536.png\" alt=\"AmfibLobsterEvoGlove_hero\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/AmfibLobsterEvoGlove_hero-1536x1536.png 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/AmfibLobsterEvoGlove_hero-297x297.png 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/AmfibLobsterEvoGlove_hero-120x120.png 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/AmfibLobsterEvoGlove_hero-768x768.png 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/AmfibLobsterEvoGlove_hero.png 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Will Pearl Izumi possibly return to higher footwear? </em>Their newest offering, the Expedition Pro shoes, looks promising, but they need that extra push, and that could be on the way. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Josh-Lawton-LV-Camp-211-scaled.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1704\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Josh-Lawton-LV-Camp-211-scaled.webp\" alt=\"From the Ground Up – Leadville Trail 100 MTB Camp\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Josh-Lawton-LV-Camp-211-scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Josh-Lawton-LV-Camp-211-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Josh-Lawton-LV-Camp-211-1536x1022.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Josh-Lawton-LV-Camp-211-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Josh-Lawton-LV-Camp-211-768x511.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Josh-Lawton-LV-Camp-211-2048x1363.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Josh-Lawton-LV-Camp-211-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Josh-Lawton-LV-Camp-211-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a><figcaption>Enzo Moscarella, Roberta Nuñez, and Shawna Anderson participate in the Leadville Trail 100 MTB Camp July 1-4, 2021. The three riders are part of the “From the Ground Up” project led by professional riders Alexey Vermeulen and Ryan Petry.</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Lastly, it wouldn’t be a podcast with Alexey if we didn’t discuss the dog in the room: Willie. We discuss how he became so comfortable on the bike and how Willie trains.<br /><br /><em>What’s the longest ride Willie does? Listen to find out! </em></p>\n\n\n\n<figure><div>\n<div><blockquote><div> <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/DIhUJ5uu0CU/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading\" target=\"_blank\"> <div> <div></div> <div> <div></div> <div></div></div></div><div></div> <div></div><div> <div>View this post on Instagram</div></div><div></div> <div><div> <div></div> <div></div> <div></div></div><div> <div></div> <div></div></div><div> <div></div> <div></div> <div></div></div></div> <div> <div></div> <div></div></div></a><p><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/DIhUJ5uu0CU/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading\" target=\"_blank\">A post shared by Alexey Vermeulen (@alexeyvermeulen)</a></p></div></blockquote></div>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<h4><span>Explore all the gear and more at <a href=\"https://www.pearlizumi.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Pearl Izumi.com</a></span>.<br /></h4>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Want More?</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Find every episode of the BikeRumor Podcast on <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/bikerumor-podcast/id1455519558\" target=\"_blank\">Apple Podcasts</a>, <a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/show/6CJD6UAmN9OHfttF4e9lx1\" target=\"_blank\">Spotify</a>, <a href=\"https://bikerumor.podbean.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Podbean</a>, and more. Or through <a href=\"https://feed.podbean.com/bikerumor/feed.xml\" target=\"_blank\">RSS</a>, or wherever you listen to podcasts! </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong><em>Hit like, hit subscribe, and hit play!</em></strong></p>